# install NodeRED on Raspberry pi

- ref: https://nodered.org/docs/getting-started/raspberrypi
- 下指令：`bash <(curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/node-red/linux-installers/master/deb/update-nodejs-and-nodered)`
- 這樣將會
  - 把目前的Node-RED停止
  - 移除Node-RED, Node.js
  - 裝Node.js 18 LTS (我安裝當下是這樣)
  - 裝Node_RED core 3.1.0
  - 裝rpi專屬的node元件
